<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Newsletter Notification</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .brand {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 100%;
        display: flex;
        flex-flow: column;
        align-items: center;
        margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    .brand img {
        width: 5rem;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #fff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    h1 {
      color: #007bff;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    p {
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .illustration {
    	width: 100%
    }

    .unsubscribe-btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 4rem;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #ffbf00;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }

    .footer {
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="brand">
        <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dirwr8cde/image/upload/v1707169188/Amitt/amitt-logo_vcdjre.png" alt="amitt logo">
        <h3>AMITT CONSULTING LIMITED</h3>
    </div>
    <h1>Welcome to Our Newsletter!</h1>
    <p>Dear {{name}},</p>
    <p>We are thrilled to have you as part of our community. Get ready for a wealth of career insights and exciting job opportunities coming your way.</p>
    <p>Stay tuned for valuable content that will empower your career journey and keep you informed about the latest trends in the job market.</p>

    <img class="illustration" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dirwr8cde/image/upload/v1707168711/Amitt/recruitment_pno4ms.jpg" alt="recruitment illustration">

    <!-- Unsubscribe Button -->
    <a href={{unsubscribeLink}} class="unsubscribe-btn">Unsubscribe</a>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>If you have any questions or concerns, please contact us at info@amittconsulting.co.uk.</p>
      <p>Thank you for being a part of our community!</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
